{"tid":496314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[慎入支那01]乘客嘆搭的士受氣　司機反批「的士優質　乘客不優質」","createTime":"2017-12-11T14:43:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T16:13:05.000Z","uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e1bdd5ec12c6266bc62bd77dd2a6785d471121d8","tid":496314,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T14:43:04.000Z","msg":"‧ 乘的士無非是為了方便快捷舒適，揮一揮手按錶收費，不過未知從何時開始，乘客踏上的士前不時要討價還價，截到車也不代表可上車， 致使Uber湧現。<br />\n<br />\n‧ 消委會建議，港府循序漸進開放網約車市場；政府亦提出引入收費更高的「優質的士」牌照，建議隨之惹來業界反彈。<br />\n<br />\n‧ 要化解雙方矛盾，只否只靠引入競爭即可？乘客和司機所求的，又是甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040429/xlarge/a1e882942e61d253e8ae1059193747be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040429%2Fxlarge%2Fa1e882942e61d253e8ae1059193747be.jpg&h=acbcc759&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消委會早前建議，港府開放網約車市場，惹來的士業界不滿。<br />\n<br />\n有市民批評的士司機態度差劣，甚至會「兜路」、拒載，贊成引入競爭。的士司機解釋，「兜路」是為了避開塞車，乘客口中的「拒載」則是剛巧碰上交更時間。司機更反指曾遭乘客以粗言穢語對待：「誰說的士不優質？不優質是乘客不優質！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040396/xlarge/9602a65a7daf92f449d713ea9b80895f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040396%2Fxlarge%2F9602a65a7daf92f449d713ea9b80895f.jpg&h=32798fb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張小姐稱，不少的士司機兜錯路，或兜很大個圈，以欺騙金錢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040393/xlarge/736fc06b72f67b7016eeb3c427087ed7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040393%2Fxlarge%2F736fc06b72f67b7016eeb3c427087ed7.jpg&h=818bd91f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n關小姐指，的士司機態度惡劣，令她非常生氣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040389/xlarge/febcebef9fc16245e7fb43d3c2bf0024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040389%2Fxlarge%2Ffebcebef9fc16245e7fb43d3c2bf0024.jpg&h=c7e7d7a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n市民唐小姐批評，的士司機經常「揀客」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040398/xlarge/dc85d6a04b98330da14bae24a78acc08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040398%2Fxlarge%2Fdc85d6a04b98330da14bae24a78acc08.jpg&h=c5803f76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n程婆婆說，遇過沒有禮貌的的士司機，催促她快點下車，不要阻礙司機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040363/xlarge/b0e95b4c5f334d831879003e1e5799d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040363%2Fxlarge%2Fb0e95b4c5f334d831879003e1e5799d9.jpg&h=e69bfcaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n的士司機翁先生認為，乘客要求多多，形容「的士優質，乘客不優質」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040378/xlarge/2eed6b4ad6c52ebeeb282091f8072128.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040378%2Fxlarge%2F2eed6b4ad6c52ebeeb282091f8072128.jpg&h=383902c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n的士司機李先生直言，香港不時塞車，「兜路」是必須的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040384/xlarge/4addf171621f4cdd7e27ac9cac7db18a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040384%2Fxlarge%2F4addf171621f4cdd7e27ac9cac7db18a.jpg&h=da88636d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n的士司機李先生認為，只要態度良好，便能減少與乘客爭執。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040406/xlarge/68ccb87f134ebea24d319e01fa363191.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040406%2Fxlarge%2F68ccb87f134ebea24d319e01fa363191.jpg&h=1ea326c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有9年經驗的的士司機林先生說，行內的確是良莠不齊，望成立委員會監管業界。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要化解雙方矛盾，是否只靠引入競爭就可？業界提倡政府仿傚保險業，透過成立委員會監管服務質素，而非假手於人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/139766/-%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E5%98%86%E6%90%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%97%E6%B0%A3-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E5%8F%8D%E6%89%B9-%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E5%84%AA%E8%B3%AA-%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E4%B8%8D%E5%84%AA%E8%B3%AA-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F139766%2F-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%2589%2587-%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%2598%2586%25E6%2590%25AD%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%25B0%25A3-%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%258F%258D%25E6%2589%25B9-%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%2584%25AA%25E8%25B3%25AA-%25E4%25B9%2598%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2584%25AA%25E8%25B3%25AA-&d=FbdMh5f%2FKkb97iUAaJbbUv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=636fd37a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/139766/-%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87-%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E5%98%86%E6%90%AD%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E5%8F%97%E6%B0%A3-%E5%8F%B8%E6%A9%9F%E5%8F%8D%E6%89%B9-%E7%9A%84%E5%A3%AB%E5%84%AA%E8%B3%AA-%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%E4%B8%8D%E5%84%AA%E8%B3%AA-</a>"},{"pid":"2ebe2193812397fe43d82fd876d822672af5473a","tid":496314,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T14:43:49.000Z","msg":"的士狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5994f71fbaf38811418d57ddb9cf50d88de14fed","tid":496314,"uid":104268,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T14:45:08.000Z","msg":"屌你老母呀的士狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa254865558ac65c18a365bbcb1abd93c95f08a0","tid":496314,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T14:47:25.000Z","msg":"的士狗兜路應該係由乘客去決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b9aaaa7fb08ceb3e25cc154f8421c6eb8993533","tid":496314,"uid":61529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T14:49:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>的士狗兜路應該係由乘客去決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n通常好既的士佬都係啲退咗休得閒無聊搵吓野做既人"},{"pid":"1a4bbab20df4bc54df7eb3a5934b343b891136ce","tid":496314,"uid":13724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T14:51:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>的士狗兜路應該係由乘客去決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>咪係，依家google map睇到晒，我上次個的士佬聽到我講電話話趕緊去醫院，我一開google map見到成條窩打老道紅色同個的士佬講，佢都話你趕去醫院行另一條路遠少少但唔塞o唔ok。司機同人哋講聲先會好好多，人哋話唔兜照塞咪又係跳錶，佢照俾錢嘅"},{"pid":"caaf22d10ac6960b9b374b10017eaf192e20a038","tid":496314,"uid":31098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T15:40:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040363/xlarge/b0e95b4c5f334d831879003e1e5799d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040363%2Fxlarge%2Fb0e95b4c5f334d831879003e1e5799d9.jpg&h=e69bfcaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n的士司機翁先生認為，乘客要求多多，形容「的士優質，乘客不優質」。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗所謂嘅「要求」﹐係要坐過海，「唔識路」囉<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040378/xlarge/2eed6b4ad6c52ebeeb282091f8072128.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040378%2Fxlarge%2F2eed6b4ad6c52ebeeb282091f8072128.jpg&h=383902c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n的士司機李先生直言，香港不時塞車，「兜路」是必須的。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你同個客好聲好氣講聲，塞車要兜路係無問題喎"},{"pid":"6f62fa94459463322ed9a659bacfdb75eb8df850","tid":496314,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T16:13:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1040406/xlarge/68ccb87f134ebea24d319e01fa363191.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1040406%2Fxlarge%2F68ccb87f134ebea24d319e01fa363191.jpg&h=1ea326c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}